SUMMARY:MomCo PDX - Meetup
DESCRIPTION:MomCo is a supportive community of moms seeking connection\, growth\, and a breath of fresh air. We meet regularly at Grace City Portland for a more structured and routine time together\, with childcare provided through our trusted KidsCo team. \nA typical meetup might include dropping off the kids at KidsCo\, mingling over coffee or tea\, enjoying a light breakfast while catching up\, engaging in a creative or fun activity\, learning from a video or guest speaker\, and wrapping up with time for reflection and meaningful discussion. Whether you’re navigating early motherhood or simply looking for authentic connection\, we’d love to have you join us as we build something new\, life-giving\, and lasting together. \nWe meet every 1st and 3rd Friday of every month with fun playdates and Mom’s Night Out in-between. Come check us out!
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/momco-pdx-meetup-2/2026-03-20/
LOCATION:Grace City Portland\, 238 NE Mason St\, Portland\, OR\, 97211\, United States
CATEGORIES:Indoor,Kids Calendar,Playgroup,Support Groups
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Screenshot-2025-11-23-at-1.18.15-PM.png
ORGANIZER;CN="MomCo":MAILTO:pccmomco@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
