SUMMARY:Paper Cup Projectors for Ramadan at FLIP
DESCRIPTION:Join us in making Paper Cup Projectors in honor of Ramadan\, starting March 11th\, at The FLIP Children’s Museum of Hillsboro. This easy\, but novel craft is great for kids\, young and old. When done\, all it takes is a phone flashlight to project the image of the crescent moon (and whatever else they draw) onto the wall. \nThis activity is included with your admission. $10/Person\, Under 2 Free. While you visit\, enjoy the rest FLIP has to offer\, including our cartoon-making room and green screen stage. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/paper-cup-projectors-for-ramadan-at-flip/2026-03-20/
